		<ipcEntry kind="c" symbol="F28" ipcLevel="C" entryType="K" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
			<textBody><title>
					<titlePart><text>HEAT EXCHANGE IN GENERAL</text>
					</titlePart>
				</title>
			</textBody>
			<ipcEntry kind="n" symbol="F28" entryType="K" ipcLevel="C" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
				<textBody>
					<note type="number">
						<noteParagraph><text>Apparatus using heat exchange or heat transfer (as defined below) for specific purposes is classified either in sub-class <sref ref="F28B" refType="/" refLevel="c"/> or in the appropriate sub-classes of, for example, classes <sref ref="F22" refType="/" refLevel="c"/>, <sref ref="F24" refType="/" refLevel="c"/>, <sref ref="F25" refType="/" refLevel="c"/>, <sref ref="F26" refType="/" refLevel="c"/>, or <sref ref="F27" refType="/" refLevel="c"/>; if no such other sub-class is appropriate, such apparatus is classified in sub-clas <sref ref="F28C" refType="/" refLevel="c"/> or <sref ref="F28D" refType="/" refLevel="c"/>.</text>
						</noteParagraph>
						<noteParagraph><text>In this class, the following terms are used with the meanings indicated:</text>
							<subnote type="alpha">
								<noteParagraph><text>"Heat exchange" means the heating or cooling of a fluid or fluent solid by direct or indirect contact with a heated or cooled fluid or fluent solid.</text>
								</noteParagraph>
								<noteParagraph><text>"Heat transfer" means the heating or cooling of a fluid or fluent solid by direct contact with a heated or cooled surface or body.</text>
								</noteParagraph>
							</subnote>
						</noteParagraph>
					</note>
				</textBody>
			</ipcEntry>
			<ipcEntry kind="u" symbol="F28D" ipcLevel="C" entryType="K" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
				<textBody><title>
						<titlePart><text>HEAT-EXCHANGE APPARATUS, NOT PROVIDED FOR IN ANOTHER SUB-CLASS, IN WHICH THE HEAT-EXCHANGE MEDIA DO NOT COME INTO DIRECT CONTACT</text>
							<entryReference>fluid heaters having heat generating means and heat transferring means <sref ref="F24H" refType="/" refLevel="c"></sref>
							</entryReference>
							<entryReference>furnaces <sref ref="F27" refType="/" refLevel="c"></sref>
							</entryReference>
							<entryReference>details of heat-exchange apparatus of general application <sref ref="F28F" refType="/" refLevel="c"></sref>
							</entryReference>
						</titlePart>
					</title>
				</textBody>
				<ipcEntry kind="g" symbol="F28D0001000000" endSymbol="F28D0005000000" entryType="K" ipcLevel="C" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
					<textBody><title>
							<titlePart><text>Heat-exchange apparatus with stationary conduit assemblies for one heat-exchange medium only, the media being in contact with different sides of the conduit wall</text>
							</titlePart>
						</title>
					</textBody>
				</ipcEntry>
				<ipcEntry kind="m" symbol="F28D0001000000" ipcLevel="C" entryType="K" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
					<textBody><title>
							<titlePart><text>Heat-exchange apparatus in which one heat-exchange medium is a large body of fluid</text>
								<entryReference><sref ref="F28D0005000000" refType="/" refLevel="c"></sref> takes precedence</entryReference>
							</titlePart>
						</title>
					</textBody>
					<ipcEntry kind="1" symbol="F28D0001020000" ipcLevel="C" entryType="K" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
						<textBody><title>
								<titlePart><text>with the heat-exchange conduits immersed in the body of fluid, e.g. with plate-like or laminated conduits</text>
								</titlePart>
							</title>
						</textBody>
						<ipcEntry kind="2" symbol="F28D0001040000" ipcLevel="C" entryType="K" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
							<textBody><title>
									<titlePart><text>with tubular conduits</text>
									</titlePart>
								</title>
							</textBody>
						</ipcEntry>
					</ipcEntry>
					<ipcEntry kind="1" symbol="F28D0001060000" ipcLevel="C" entryType="K" isRenumbered="N" isDead="N" lang="EN" noadvanced="yes">
						<textBody><title>
								<titlePart><text>with the heat-exchange conduits forming part of, or being attached to, the tank containing the body of fluid</text>
								</titlePart>
							</title>
						</textBody>
					</ipcEntry>
				</ipcEntry>
